quran[12]{c,v,t}:
  27,77,aur be shak yeh mominoun ke liye Hadayat aur rehmat hai
  27,78,tumhara perwar-digaar ( qayamat ke roz ) unn mein apne hukum se faisla kar day ga aur woh ghalib ( aur ) ilm wala hai
  27,79,to khuda par bharosa rakho tum to haq Sarih par ho
  27,80,kuch shak nahi ke tum mardon ko ( baat ) nahi suna satke aur nah behroon ko jab ke woh peeth phair kar phir jayen aawaz suna satke ho
  27,81,aur nah andhon ko gumraahi se ( nikaal kar ) rasta dekha satke ho. tum un hi ko suna satke ho jo hamari aayton par imaan laatay hain aur woh farmanbardar ho jatay hain
  27,82,aur jab unn ke baray mein ( azaab ) ka wada poora hoga to hum unn ke liye zameen mein se aik janwar nikalen ge jo un se bayan kar day ga. is liye ke log hamari aayton par imaan nahi laatay they
  27,83,aur jis roz hum har aُmt mein se is giroh ko jama karen ge jo hamari aayton ki takzieeb karte they to unn ki jamaat bandi ki jaye gi
  27,84,yahan taq ke jab ( sab ) ajayeen ge to ( khuda ) farmaiye ga kekiya tum ne meri aayton ko jhutla diya tha aur tum ne ( apne ) ilm se un par ihata tokiya hi nah tha. bhala tumkiya karte they
  27,85,aur unn ke zulm ke sabab unn ke haq mein wada ( azaab ) poora hokar rahay ga to woh bol bhi nah saken ge
  27,86,kiya onhon ne nahi dekha ke hum ne raat ko ( is liye ) banaya hai ke is mein aaraam karen aur din ko roshan ( banaya hai ke is mein kaam karen ) be shak is mein momin logon ke liye nishanain hain
  27,87,aur jis roz sor phonka jaye ga to jo log asmano aur zameen mein hain sab ghabra uthen ge magar woh jisay khuda chahay aur sab is ke paas aajiz ho kar chalay ayen ge
  27,88,aur tum pahoron ko dekhte ho to khayaal karte ho ke ( apni jagah par ) kharray hain magar woh ( is roz ) is terhan uday phrin ge jaisay baadal. ( yeh ) khuda ki karigari hai jis ne har cheez ko mazboot banaya. be shak woh tumahray sab af-aal se bakhabar hai
